OL,3,CWarning after family scammed by
OL,4,C'nasty' Facebook holiday advert
OL,6,FA family from Cornwall say they are
OL,7,F'gutted' after being scammed out of a
OL,8,Fholiday on Facebook.
OL,10,FDave Pengelly and his partner Kathy,
OL,11,Fwere excited after seeing a cheap deal
OL,12,Fon the social media platform for a
OL,13,Fcaravan at Looe Bay Holiday Park.
OL,15,FThe account, which was under the name
OL,16,F"Laura", was charging a total of #325
OL,17,Ffor a long weekend.
