OL,6,FSpeaking at their family home in
OL,7,FSaltash, Dave said: "It was going to
OL,8,Fbe a nice time for the kids to have a
OL,9,Fbreak, something they hadn't had for
OL,10,Fso long.
OL,12,F"We'd been saving and scraping and
OL,13,Fgiven up doing things the house, like
OL,14,Fthe carpets, purely to pay for it.
OL,15,FIt's not so much letting my partner
OL,16,Fdown, she understands.
