OL,6,F"But trying to explain to a nine-year-
OL,7,Fold boy you cannot take them on
OL,8,Fholiday because you just don't have
OL,9,Fthe money for it now. It's gutting,
OL,10,Freally gutting you know."
OL,12,FA series of messages were exchanged
OL,13,Fbetween Dave and "Laura" - who had
OL,14,Fagreed to let him pay in instalments.
OL,15,FBut as soon as Dave made the last
OL,16,Fpayment, the account went dark.
