OL,3,CWarning after family scammed by
OL,4,C'nasty' Facebook holiday advert
OL,6,FKathy Sollick feels heartbroken that
OL,7,Fshe cannot taken her son, Charlie, on
OL,8,Fholiday. She said: "To have that
OL,9,Fsuddenly pulled from underneath you
OL,10,Fjust because there was no such
OL,11,Fcaravan, there was no such person.
OL,13,F"This person we thought we were having
OL,14,Fthe caravan from was happy to take our
OL,15,Fmoney.
OL,17,F"Then to pay the money and then have
OL,18,Fnothing, I just don't understand how
OL,19,Fpeople can just be so vile and so
OL,20,Fnasty."
