OL,3,CWarning after family scammed by
OL,4,C'nasty' Facebook holiday advert
OL,6,FLooe Bay Holiday Park has confirmed
OL,7,Fthat a number of other families have
OL,8,Fbeen affected by the Facebook scam.
OL,9,FOne family had even driven for eight
OL,10,Fhours only to find their booking did
OL,11,Fnot exist.
OL,13,FA spokesperson for the holiday park
OL,14,Fsaid: "We're concerned by these scam
OL,15,Fadverts and sympathise with anybody
OL,16,Fwho has been affected.
OL,18,F"These adverts relate to private
OL,19,Fbookings, rather than our booking
OL,20,Fplatforms.
