OL,3,CWarning after family scammed by
OL,4,C'nasty' Facebook holiday advert
OL,6,F"We would always urge anybody looking
OL,7,Fto stay at the park to securely book
OL,8,Fdirectly through our website or via
OL,9,Fone of our trusted partners."
OL,11,FFacebook has also issued advice
OL,12,Fregarding online fraud saying: "We are
OL,13,Fcontinually investing in protections
OL,14,Fagainst fraud for people who use our
OL,15,Fplatforms and work closely with law
OL,16,Fenforcement to support investigations.
OL,18,F"We encourage our community to report
OL,19,Factivity like this to us and the
OL,20,Fpolice, so we can take action."
