OL,6,FDave and Kathy did contact Devon and
OL,7,FCornwall Police and were referred to
OL,8,Fthe National Crime Agency.
OL,10,FThey have been refunded the #125
OL,11,Fdeposit, but are yet to find out if
OL,12,Ftheir banks will refund them the other
OL,13,F#200.
OL,15,FOliver Little, a detective
OL,16,Fsuperintendent with Action Fraud,
OL,17,Fwants to encourage anyone who believes
OL,18,Fthey have been scammed to report it.
