OL,3,CWarning after family scammed by
OL,4,C'nasty' Facebook holiday advert
OL,6,FHe explained: "We see peaks of travel
OL,7,Ffraud in the summer months, which
OL,8,Fleave people empty handed. Fraudsters
OL,9,Foften ask for a bank transfer, not a
OL,10,Fcredit or debit card, so that is a red
OL,11,Fflag.
OL,13,F"People can feel embarrassed to report
OL,14,Fto the police, but we do have a
OL,15,Fdedicated team of professionals who
OL,16,Fwork to locate these harmful accounts
OL,17,Fand adverts.
OL,19,F"We want to shut them down and get
OL,20,Fthem taken off. Reporting could help
OL,21,Fothers from falling victim."
